2006 WCA Bianchi Cyclo-Cross Race #2
course: The course is approx. a 2-mile loop on the Lapham Peak State Park mountain bike trails.  Great for cyclo-cross and mountain bikes, the course features both flat and rolling sections, with short run-ups and fun downhills!
registration: Opens at 9:30 am and closes 15 min. before each event.  No pre-reg.  Entry fee includes insurance ($2), WCA ($1).  USCF rules apply. Held under USCF permit.  Open to all racers.  Cyclo-cross series points will be awarded.
directions: Lapham Peak State Park is located on Hwy. C in Delafield, WI.  Exit I-94 at Hwy C, travel South for approx. two miles, the park is on your left.  Park in the Evergreen parking lot, first right after entering the park.
